Make a WebGL canvas paint INLINE (not composited) so its output reaches the software
page paint / screenshots in this compositor-less embedder.

WebGLRenderingContextBase::IsComposited() is hardcoded true, so blink gives the canvas
a cc::Layer that only the compositor draws. miniblink-modern is single-process with a
non-compositing software paint (mbPaintToBitmap), which skips composited layers -> a
WebGL canvas renders to its drawing buffer (gl.readPixels works) but is BLANK in
screenshots. Returning false routes the canvas through HTMLCanvasElement::PaintInternal
-> PaintRenderingResultsToSnapshot(kFrontBuffer), which reads the GPU drawing buffer
back to a CPU bitmap and draws it inline -> WebGL composites into the page paint. This
is the correct behavior for headless capture; the CHECK(context_->IsComposited()) paths
are all gated on IsRenderingContext2D(), so WebGL is unaffected by them.

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.h b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.h
index 6fa192f..14a7a1a 100644
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.h
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.h
@@ -709,7 +709,13 @@ class MODULES_EXPORT WebGLRenderingContextBase
       SourceDrawingBuffer);
 
   // CanvasRenderingContext implementation.
-  bool IsComposited() const override { return true; }
+  // miniblink-modern: a WebGL canvas is normally composited (a cc_layer the
+  // compositor draws). This embedder has NO compositor (single-process software
+  // paint), so a composited canvas is skipped at paint time and screenshots show it
+  // blank. Returning false routes the canvas through inline snapshot painting
+  // (PaintRenderingResultsToSnapshot reads the GPU drawing buffer back to a bitmap),
+  // so WebGL output composites into mbPaintToBitmap. Correct for headless capture.
+  bool IsComposited() const override { return false; }
   void PageVisibilityChanged() override;
   void SizeChanged() override;
   scoped_refptr<StaticBitmapImage> PaintRenderingResultsToSnapshot(
